(26127, 'robinul', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Concomitant administration of ROBINUL Injection and potassium chloride in a wax matrix may increase the severity of potassium chloride-induced gastrointestinal lesions as a result of a slower gastrointestinal transit time.', 'DailyMed'),
